OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMany places will have a dry day
OL,6,Falthough the odd shower possible
OL,7,Facross the far west. Some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells breaking through at
OL,9,Ftimes, more especially along the north
OL,10,Fcoast. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe east will be dry with a
OL,13,Ffew clear periods overnight. Dumfries
OL,14,Fand Galloway will be cloudy with some
OL,15,Fpatchy rain, mainly over the hills.
OL,16,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
