OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEdinburgh, Lothian and
OL,6,Feastern Borders mainly dry with some
OL,7,Foccasional brightness. Dumfries,
OL,8,FGalloway and western Boders cloudy
OL,9,Fwith rain at times. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FUnsettled with showers or longer
OL,13,Fspells of rain on Thursday. Chance of
OL,14,Frain at first on Friday, otherwise
OL,15,Fbright with a few showers. Rain
OL,16,Fspreading east later Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
